itunes:title: #93 - Jasmine Star on Authenticity and Haters
title: #93 - Jasmine Star on Authenticity and Haters
description:
Jasmine Star is on Being Boss today! Jasmine became one of the most sought after photographers in California in 2007, and in 2009 she was named on of the top 10 wedding photographers in the world. This was only after starting her photography business in 2006. Now she provides coaching for other creative businesses so we've got a lot to talk about scaling a business, shifting focus, and dealing with that inner critic and haters.

—

Listen to more Being Boss shows on our website, on Apple Podcasts, or wherever you listen to podcasts.
